Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:44.93,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}悟り-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:50.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}声にならぬ晴天を見た
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:55.22,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}眩しい朝日に負けない眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:22:02.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}何度壊されたって　It's a hard intention like a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:05.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}また積み上げてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:08.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Undying-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:12.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}何故か探り合ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:18.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}駆け引きなんて自分を惑わしては
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:25.76,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}見失ってまた拾い集めてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:29.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ああ　繰り返すのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:31.15,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}微か…聞こえる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:36.88,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}誰かの笑い声　誰かの泣き声が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:39.31,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}今、隣り合う世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.31,0:22:40.16,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}hand in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:45.04,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いつも最後には分かり合えてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:49.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ifの答えは糸口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.86,0:22:50.78,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}hand in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:55.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いつも最後には分かり合えてた
